snippet.title: Project Sphinx: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2230990/Project_Sphinx/

Project Sphinx is a first-person puzzle-solving game, in which you're a robot with a mission on a space station. And like any great robot, you're going to have to explore, teleport and ricochet your way around the base, in which each room and corridor is a puzzle to solve.
